description:
This is a 33 minute workout called '15 Minute Interval Training Treadmill Workout | Cardio & Strength to Burn Fat and Tone Up' from the channel Orbit Fitness Equipment.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Rhythm Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Can’t find the time to workout? We’ve created a quick 15-minute HIIT treadmill workout that can be modified to suit anyone. This easy to follow workout combines strength and cardio to make the most of your time by burning fat and toning simultaneously.
 
For the full written workout head to the blog: 
https://www.orbitfitness.com.au/blog/15-minute-interval-training-treadmill-workout
